snippet.textDisplay: Aside from DeNiro and Foxx, I am disgusted by the lot of them. They are acting when they're speaking and they remind me of feudal lords discussing their divine right to rule, while peasants  work their lands and do their bidding. There isn't one of them who has said something I don't  regard as complete and utter bollocks. For example, if you need to shoot a sad scene... then you just think of something fucking sad, twats - rocket science it ain't! I long for the day when these people are acting for bread and a place to sleep in the stable. I've lost count of the actual times when people like this say they aren't in it for the money. I would genuinely give my soul to see them on a working wage; we'll soon see whose 'in it for the art.' If you think I'm bitter then you'd better believe I am, baby!  because I'm sick of getting fucked over while they have everything. They put out shit after shit film THEN try to sell me their latest perfume/book/bedding/fitness video! Teachers, nurses, people that takeout the rubbish, farmers, people that stack shelves: real heroes. The only thing I can abhor worse than this video  - and the questions it raises - is myself for watching this. Goodnight fuckheads.
